ute the ISM with the hydrostatic elements. We use a simple\nchemical evolution model, flexCE to further backup our claim and conclude that\nrecent stellar generations of Fornax and the LMC could also have formed\naccording to a top-light IMF.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jul 2017 20:47:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-08-30"}
