\nstudy will help the users such as researchers or security staffs to obtain the\nTHz security images of good quality. Currently, our research group is\nattempting to make this research more comprehensive.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jul 2017 07:26:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Oct 2017 14:01:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-10-04"}
